      <scopecontent>
         
         <head>Collection Overview</head>
         
         <p>The Convocations Reference Collection was compiled from a variety of sources by the University Archives for use in reference and research. The collection includes primarily convocation programs, as well as some correspondence, flyers, and clippings relating to Opening Convocations at Duke.   </p>
      
